            <details class="testimonia-d">
               <summary>Testimonia</summary>
               <div class="testimonia"> Cf. <i>Yogasārasaṅgraha</i>, p. 54. 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">sadādināthāya namo ’stu tubhyaṃ</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">yenopadiṣṭā haṭhayogavidyā |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">virājate pronnatarājayogam</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">āroḍhum icchor adhirohiṇīva ||</p> 
                     </div>
                  <i>Gheraṇḍasaṃhitā</i> 1.1 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">ādīśvarāya praṇamāmi tasmai</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">yenopadiṣṭā haṭhayogavidyā |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">virājate pronnatarājayogam</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">āroḍhum icchor adhirohiṇīva ||</p> 
                     </div>
