      <details class="jyotsna-d">
         <summary>Jyotsna Commentary
            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               iti pūrvoktā ādayo yeṣāṃ te tathā. ādiśabdena tārānāthādayo grāhyāḥ. mahāntaś ca te
               siddhāś ca
               apratihataiśvaryā ity arthaḥ. haṭhayogasya prabhāvāt sāmarthyād iti haṭhayogaprabhāvataḥ.
               pañcamyās tasil. kālo mṛtyus tasya daṇḍanaṃ daṇḍaḥ dehaprāṇaviyogānukūlo vyāpāraḥ
               taṃ
               khaṇḍayitvā chittvā mṛtyuṃ jitvety arthaḥ. brahmāṇḍe brahmāṇḍamadhye vicaranti
               viśeṣeṇāvyāhatagatyā carantīty arthaḥ. tad uktaṃ bhāgavate
               <div class="lg">
                  <p class="versinnote">yogeśvarāṇāṃ gatim āhur antar</p>
                  <p class="versinnote">bahistrilokyāḥ pavanāntarātmanām  iti.</p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               iti pūrvoktā ādayo yeṣāṃ te tathā. ādiśabdena tārānāthādayo grāhyāḥ. mahāntaś ca te
               siddhāś ca
               apratihataiśvaryā ity arthaḥ. haṭhayogasya prabhāvāt sāmarthyād iti haṭhayogaprabhāvataḥ.
               pañcamyās tasil. kālo mṛtyus tasya daṇḍanaṃ daṇḍaḥ dehaprāṇaviyogānukūlo vyāpāraḥ
               taṃ
               khaṇḍayitvā chittvā mṛtyuṃ jitvety arthaḥ. brahmāṇḍe brahmāṇḍamadhye vicaranti
               viśeṣeṇāvyāhatagatyā carantīty arthaḥ. tad uktaṃ bhāgavate
               <div class="lg">
                  <p class="versinnote">yogeśvarāṇāṃ gatim āhur antar</p>
                  <p class="versinnote">bahistrilokyāḥ pavanāntarātmanām  iti.</p>
