      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp01_014" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 1.14</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> एवंविधे मठे स्थित्वा सर्वचिन्ता<mark>विवर्जितः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> गुरूपदिष्टमार्गेण <mark>योगमेव</mark> <mark>समभ्यसेत्</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> evaṃvidhe maṭhe sthitvā sarvacintā<mark>vivarjitaḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> gurūpadiṣṭamārgeṇa <mark>yogam eva</mark> <mark>samabhyaset</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Staying in such a hut, free from all worry, in the way taught by his guru [the yogi]
               should practise nothing but yoga. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
