               <div class="app"><span class="lem">gulphaṃ</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] gulphe (<span class="siglum" title="δ3 Lalchand M-6494">δ<sub>3</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε2 NGMPP E-1528-1 / E-1527-7(4)">ε<sub>2</sub></span>)</div>
