      <details class="jyotsna-d">
         <summary>Jyotsna Commentary
            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               gomukhāsanam āha savya iti. savye vāme pṛṣṭhasya pārśve sampradāyāt kaṭer adhobhāge
               dakṣiṇaṃ
               gulphaṃ nitarāṃ yojayet. dakṣiṇe 'pi pṛṣṭhapārśve tathā savyavat savyaṃ gulphaṃ niyojayet.
               gomukhasyākṛtir iva ākṛtir yasya tat tādṛśaṃ gomukhaṃ gomukhasaṃjñakam āsanaṃ bhavet.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               gomukhāsanam āha savya iti. savye vāme pṛṣṭhasya pārśve sampradāyāt kaṭer adhobhāge
               dakṣiṇaṃ
               gulphaṃ nitarāṃ yojayet. dakṣiṇe 'pi pṛṣṭhapārśve tathā savyavat savyaṃ gulphaṃ niyojayet.
               gomukhasyākṛtir iva ākṛtir yasya tat tādṛśaṃ gomukhaṃ gomukhasaṃjñakam āsanaṃ bhavet.
               </div>
