            <details class="testimonia-d">
               <summary>Testimonia</summary>
               <div class="testimonia"> <i>Yogacintāmaṇi</i> f. 84r (attr. <i>Haṭhapradīpikā</i>) 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">prasārya pādau bhuvi daṇḍarūpau</p>
