               śavāsanam āhārdhena uttānam iti. śavena mṛtaśarīreṇa tulyaṃ śavavad uttānaṃ
               bhūmisaṃlagnaṃ pṛṣṭhaṃ yathā syāt tathā śayanaṃ nidrāyām iva
               saṃniveśo yat tac chavāsanaṃ. śavākhyam āsanam.  śavāsanaprayojanam āha uttarārdhena.
               śavāsanaṃ
               śrāntiharaṃ śrāntiṃ haṭhābhyāsaśramaṃ haratīti śrāntiharaṃ. cittasya viśrāntir viśrāmas
               tasyāḥ
