                     <p class="versinnote">caitan mokṣakapāṭabhedajanakaṃ siddhāsanaṃ procyate ||</p>
                     <p class="versinnote"><span class="appinnote">yonisthānakam ] yonidvārakam P,T. niyataṃ ] hṛdaye T,t1,n2. °kapāṭa° ] °kavāṭa° P,T,t1</span>
