      <details class="jyotsna-d">
         <summary>Jyotsna Commentary
            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               matsyendrasammataṃ siddhāsanam uktvānyasaṃmataṃ vaktum āha matāntare tv iti. tad eva
               darśayati
               meḍhrād iti. meḍhrād upasthād upary ūrdhvabhāge savyaṃ
               vāmagulphaṃ vinyasya tathā savyavad upari
               savyapādasyopari na tu savyagulphasya. gulphāntaraṃ dakṣiṇagulphaṃ ca nikṣipya vased
               iti
               śeṣaḥ. idaṃ siddhāsanam matāntarābhimataṃ bhaved ity arthaḥ.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               matsyendrasammataṃ siddhāsanam uktvānyasaṃmataṃ vaktum āha matāntare tv iti. tad eva
               darśayati
               meḍhrād iti. meḍhrād upasthād upary ūrdhvabhāge savyaṃ
               vāmagulphaṃ vinyasya tathā savyavad upari
               savyapādasyopari na tu savyagulphasya. gulphāntaraṃ dakṣiṇagulphaṃ ca nikṣipya vased
               iti
               śeṣaḥ. idaṃ siddhāsanam matāntarābhimataṃ bhaved ity arthaḥ.
               </div>
