                  </div>
               atha saptabhiḥ ślokaiḥ siddhāsanaṃ praśaṃsati yameṣvityādibhiḥ. yameṣu mitāhāram iva.
               mitāhāro
               vakṣyamāṇaḥ susnigdhamadhurāhāra ityādinā. niyameṣu ahiṃsām iva. sarvāṇi yāny
               āsanāni teṣu siddhāḥ ekaṃ siddhāsanaṃ mukhyaṃ vidur iti sambandhaḥ.
               </div>
