            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               caturaśītīti. caturadhikāśītisaṅkhyākāni yāni pīṭhāni teṣu siddham eva siddhāsanam
               eva sadā
               sarvadābhyaset. siddhāsanasya sadābhyāse hetugarbhaviśeṣaṇaṃ. dvāsaptatisahasrāṇāṃ
