            <details class="testimonia-d">
               <summary>Testimonia</summary>
               <div class="testimonia"> <i>Yogacintāmaṇi</i> f. 85r (attr. <i>Haṭhapradīpikā</i>) 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">ātmadhyāyī mitāhārī yāvad dvādaśavatsaram |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">sadā siddhāsanābhyāsād yogī niṣpattim āpnuyāt |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">śramadair bahubhiḥ pīṭhaiḥ kiṃ syāt siddhāsane sati ||</p> 
