                  <i>Yogasārasaṅgraha</i> p. 9 (attr. <i>Yogasāramañjarī</i>) 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">ātmadhyāyo mitāhārī yāvad dvādaśavatsaram |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">sadā siddhāsanābhyāsād yoganiṣpattim āpnuyāt ||</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">śramadair bahubhiḥ pīṭhair alaṃ siddhāsane sati |</p> 
                     </div>
