      <details class="jyotsna-d">
         <summary>Jyotsna Commentary
            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               ātmadhyāyīti. ātmānaṃ dhyāyatīty ātmadhyāyī. mita āhāro
               'syāstīti mitāhārī. yāvanto dvādaśa vatsarāḥ
               yāvaddvādaśavatsaram. yāvad avadhāraṇa ity avyayībhāvaḥ samāsaḥ.
               dvādaśavatsaraparyantam ity arthaḥ. sadā sarvadā siddhāsanasyābhyāsād yogī yogābhyāsī
               niṣpattim
               yogasiddhim āpnuyāt prāpnuyāt. yogāṅgāntarābhyāsam antareṇa siddhāsanābhyāsamātreṇa
               siddhiṃ
               prāpnuyād ity arthaḥ.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               ātmadhyāyīti. ātmānaṃ dhyāyatīty ātmadhyāyī. mita āhāro
               'syāstīti mitāhārī. yāvanto dvādaśa vatsarāḥ
               yāvaddvādaśavatsaram. yāvad avadhāraṇa ity avyayībhāvaḥ samāsaḥ.
               dvādaśavatsaraparyantam ity arthaḥ. sadā sarvadā siddhāsanasyābhyāsād yogī yogābhyāsī
               niṣpattim
               yogasiddhim āpnuyāt prāpnuyāt. yogāṅgāntarābhyāsam antareṇa siddhāsanābhyāsamātreṇa
               siddhiṃ
               prāpnuyād ity arthaḥ.
               </div>
         </div>
      </details>
   </div>
   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp01_041" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 1.41</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>प्राणानिले</mark> <mark>सावधानं</mark> <mark>बद्धे</mark> <mark>केवलकुम्भके</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>उत्पद्यते</mark> निरायासा<mark>त्स्वयमेवोन्मनी</mark> <mark>यथा</mark> ॥ 
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>prāṇānile</mark> <mark>sāvadhānaṃ</mark> <mark>baddhe</mark> <mark>kevalakumbhake</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>utpadyate</mark> nirāyāsā<mark>t svayam evonmanī</mark> <mark>yathā</mark> // 
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Just as the [state] beyond mind (<i>unmanī</i>) arises automatically, without effort, when the <i>prāṇa</i> breath has been carefully stopped in <i>kevalakumbhaka</i>, [...] </div>
