                  <p class="hpvers"> bhadrāsanaṃ bhaved etat sarvavyādhi<mark>viṣāpaham</mark> / </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> gorakṣāsanam ity āhur i<mark>daṃ</mark> <mark>vai siddhayoginaḥ</mark> //</p> 
