   <div class="altrec">
      <div class="main">
         <div class="hpmeta">
            <div class="text">
               <div id="hp01_055_2" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 1.55*2</span><div class="versdev">
                     <p class="hpvers"> न <mark>वेषधारणं</mark> <mark>सिद्धेः</mark> कारणं <mark>न च</mark> <mark>तत्कथा</mark> । </p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> क्रियैव कारणं <mark>सिद्धेः</mark> सत्य<mark>मेत</mark>न्न संशयः । </p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> <mark>शिश्नोदर</mark><mark>रतायेह</mark> <mark>न</mark> <mark>देया</mark> <mark>वेष</mark><mark>धारिणः</mark> ॥ <span class="inlineref">(<span class="siglum" title="β2 Lalchand M-2089">β<sub>2</sub></span>, <span class="siglum" title="βω Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 29899">β<sub>ω</sub></span>, <span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span> and <span class="siglum" title="χ Brahmānanda’s version">χ</span>)</span>
                        </p>
                     </div>
                  <div class="versltn">
                     <p class="hpvers"> na <mark>veṣadhāraṇaṃ</mark> <mark>siddheḥ</mark> kāraṇaṃ <mark>na ca</mark> <mark>tatkathā</mark> / </p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> kriyaiva kāraṇaṃ <mark>siddheḥ</mark> satya<mark>m eta</mark>n na saṃśayaḥ / </p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> <mark>śiśnodara</mark><mark>ratāyeha</mark> <mark>na</mark> <mark>deyā</mark> <mark>veṣa</mark><mark>dhāriṇaḥ</mark> // <span class="inlineref">(<span class="siglum" title="β2 Lalchand M-2089">β<sub>2</sub></span>, <span class="siglum" title="βω Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 29899">β<sub>ω</sub></span>, <span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span> and <span class="siglum" title="χ Brahmānanda’s version">χ</span>)</span>
                        </p>
                     </div>
               </div>
               <div class="translation"> Wearing a robe does not bring about success, nor does talking [about yoga]. Practice
                  alone is the cause of success. This is true, there is no doubt. In this system, [the
                  practice] should not be given to one who wears robes and is devoted to sex and food.
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="crit">
