               sūryabhedanam ujjāyī ityādivakṣyamāṇam. mudrā ity akhyā yasya tat mudrākhyam
               mahāmudrādirūpaṃ karaṇaṃ haṭhasiddhau prakṛṣṭopakārakam. tathā
