                     <p class="hpvers">सर्वशाकमचाक्षुष्यं <mark>चाक्षुष्यं</mark> शाकपञ्चकं ।</p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> जीवन्ती वास्तु मत्स्याक्षी मेघनादः पुनर्नवा ॥ <span class="inlineref">(<span class="siglum" title="γ1 NGMPP G 25-2 γ1ac γ1pc">γ<sub>1</sub></span>)</span>
                        </p> 
                     </div>
                  <div class="versltn">
                     <p class="hpvers">sarvaśākamacākṣuṣyaṃ <mark>cākṣuṣyaṃ</mark> śākapañcakaṃ /</p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> jīvantī vāstu matsyākṣī meghanādaḥ punarnavā // <span class="inlineref">(<span class="siglum" title="γ1 NGMPP G 25-2 γ1ac γ1pc">γ<sub>1</sub></span>)</span>
