               <div class="app"><span class="lem">ante prathamo° add.</span>āsanayogo nāma (<span class="siglum" title="ε3 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30051 ε3ac ε3pc">ε<sub>3</sub></span>), āsanavidhikathanaṃ nāma (<span class="siglum" title="χ Brahmānanda’s version">χ</span>)</div>
