      <details class="jyotsna-d">
         <summary>Jyotsna Commentary
            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               prayojanam anuddiśya na mando 'pi pravartate iti mahadukteḥ prayojanābhāve pravṛttyabhāvāt
               prāṇāyāmaprayojanam āha cale vāte iti. vāte cale sati cittaṃ calaṃ bhavet. niścale
               vāte niścalaṃ
               bhavet cittam ity atrāpi sambadhyate. vāte citte ca niścale yogī sthāṇutvaṃ sthiratvaṃ
               dīrghajīvitvam iti yāvat. īśatvaṃ vāpnoti. tatas tasmād vāyuṃ prāṇaṃ nirodhayet kumbhayet.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               prayojanam anuddiśya na mando 'pi pravartate iti mahadukteḥ prayojanābhāve pravṛttyabhāvāt
               prāṇāyāmaprayojanam āha cale vāte iti. vāte cale sati cittaṃ calaṃ bhavet. niścale
               vāte niścalaṃ
               bhavet cittam ity atrāpi sambadhyate. vāte citte ca niścale yogī sthāṇutvaṃ sthiratvaṃ
               dīrghajīvitvam iti yāvat. īśatvaṃ vāpnoti. tatas tasmād vāyuṃ prāṇaṃ nirodhayet kumbhayet.
               </div>
