               ucyate lokaiḥ.
               dehaprāṇasaṃyogasyaiva jīvanapadārthatvāt. tasya prāṇasya niṣkrāntir dehād viyogaḥ
               maraṇam ucyate.
               tatas tasmād vāyuṃ nirodhayet.
               </div>
