   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_004" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.4</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>मलाकुलासु</mark> नाडीषु मारुतो नैव मध्यगः ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> कथं स्यादुन्मनीभावः <mark>कायसिद्धिः</mark> कथं भवेत् ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>malākulāsu</mark> nāḍīṣu māruto naiva madhyagaḥ /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> kathaṃ syād unmanībhāvaḥ <mark>kāyasiddhiḥ</mark> kathaṃ bhavet //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> When the channels are full of impurities, the breath does not go into the middle.
               How would the state beyond mind occur? How would perfection of the body arise? </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">malākulāsu</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] mālākusuma (<span class="siglum" title="η1 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30109 η1ac η1pc">η<sub>1</sub></span>)</div>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">kāyasiddhiḥ</span> (<span class="siglum" title="α1 NGMPP B 62-20 α1ac α1pc">α<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="α3 GOML 18885">α<sub>3</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="β2 Lalchand M-2089">β<sub>2</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="βω Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 29899">β<sub>ω</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε3 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30051 ε3ac ε3pc">ε<sub>3</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="η1 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30109 η1ac η1pc">η<sub>1</sub></span>) ] kāyaśuddhiḥ (<span class="siglum" title="Γ N23,J7">Γ</span>), kāryasiddhiḥ (<span class="siglum" title="β1">β<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="Δ V19,K3,C7">Δ</span> <span class="siglum" title="ε1">ε<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="χ Brahmānanda’s version">χ</span>)</div>
