      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_005" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.5</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>शुद्धिमेति</mark> <mark>यदा</mark> सर्वं नाडी<mark>चक्रं</mark> <mark>मलाकुलम्</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>तदैव</mark> जायते योगी प्राण<mark>संग्रहणे</mark> क्षमः ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>śuddhim eti</mark> <mark>yadā</mark> sarvaṃ nāḍī<mark>cakraṃ</mark> <mark>malākulam</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>tadaiva</mark> jāyate yogī prāṇa<mark>saṃgrahaṇe</mark> kṣamaḥ //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Only when the entire impure network of channels is cleansed is the yogi able to control
               the breath. </div>
