               ākulam
               vyāptaṃ sarvaṃ samastaṃ nāḍīnāṃ cakraṃ samūhaḥ śuddhim malarāhityam eti prāpnoti tadaiva
               tasminn
               eva kāle yogī yogābhyāsī prāṇasya samyag grahaṇe kṣamaḥ samartho jāyate.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
