      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_007" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.7</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> बद्ध<mark>पद्मासनो</mark> योगी प्राणं चन्द्रेण <mark>पूरयेत्</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> धारयित्वा यथा<mark>शक्त्या</mark> <mark>पुनः</mark> सूर्येण रेचयेत् ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> baddha<mark>padmāsano</mark> yogī prāṇaṃ candreṇa <mark>pūrayet</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> dhārayitvā yathā<mark>śaktyā</mark> <mark>punaḥ</mark> sūryeṇa recayet //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Seated in the lotus pose, the yogi should fill himself up with air via the moon [channel],
               hold it for as long as he can, then expel it through the sun [channel]. </div>
         </div>
