   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_008" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.8</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> प्राणं सूर्येण <mark>चाकृष्य</mark> पूरये<mark>दुदरं</mark> शनैः ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>विधिव</mark>त्कुम्भकं <mark>कृत्वा</mark> पुनश्चन्द्रेण रेचयेत् ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> prāṇaṃ sūryeṇa <mark>cākṛṣya</mark> pūraye<mark>d udaraṃ</mark> śanaiḥ /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>vidhiva</mark>t kumbhakaṃ <mark>kṛtvā</mark> punaś candreṇa recayet //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> And, drawing the breath through the sun [channel], he should gradually fill the abdomen.
               Having performed the retention as prescribed, he should then exhale through the moon
               [channel]. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
