      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_016" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.16</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> प्राणायामेन युक्तेन सर्वरोग<mark>क्षयो भवेत्</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> अयुक्ताभ्यासयोगेन सर्व<mark>रोग</mark><mark>समुद्भवः</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> prāṇāyāmena yuktena sarvaroga<mark>kṣayo bhavet</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> ayuktābhyāsayogena sarva<mark>roga</mark><mark>samudbhavaḥ</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> All diseases are destroyed by correct <i>prāṇāyāma</i>. As a result of incorrect practice any disease may arise. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
