   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_018" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.18</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark></mark>युक्तं युक्तं त्यजेद्वायुं युक्तं युक्तं च <mark>पूरयेत्</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> युक्तं युक्तं <mark>च</mark> बध्नीयाद् ए<mark>वं</mark> <mark>शुद्धिमवाप्नुयात्</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark></mark>yuktaṃ yuktaṃ tyajed vāyuṃ yuktaṃ yuktaṃ ca <mark>pūrayet</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> yuktaṃ yuktaṃ <mark>ca</mark> badhnīyād e<mark>vaṃ</mark> <mark>śuddhim avāpnuyāt</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> [The yogi] should exhale correctly, inhale correctly and hold the breath correctly.
               He thus becomes purified. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
