            <details class="sources-d">
               <summary>Sources</summary>
               <div class="sources"> <i>Vivekamārtaṇḍa</i> 101 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">yatheṣṭaṃ dhāraṇāṃ vāyor analasya pradīpanam |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">nādābhivyaktir ārogyaṃ jāyate nāḍīśodhanāt ||</p> 
                     </div>
