               karmāṇi nācaret.
               tatra hetum āha doṣāṇāṃ vātapittakaphānāṃ samasya bhāvaḥ samabhāvaḥ samatvaṃ tasmād
               doṣāṇāṃ
               samatvād ity arthaḥ.
