               <summary>Testimonia</summary>
               <div class="testimonia"> <i>Haṭharatnāvalī</i> 1.37–38ab 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">atha dhautiḥ--</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">viṃśaddhastapramāṇena dhautavastraṃ sudīrghitam |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">caturaṅgulavistāraṃ siktaṃ caiva śanaiḥ graset ||</p>
