                  <i>Yogacintāmaṇi</i> f.~71r (attr.~to the <i>Haṭhapradīpikā</i>) 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">atha dhautī |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">caturaṅgulavistāraṃ siktaṃ vastraṃ śanair graset |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">punaḥ pratyāhared etad abhyāsād dhautikarmavit ||</p> 
                     </div>
                  <i>Yuktabhavadeva</i> 7.150 (attr.~to the <i>Haṭhapradīpikā</i>) 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">caturaṃgulavistāraṃ siktaṃ vastraṃ śanair graset |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">tataḥ pratyāharec caitad ākṣālaṃ dhautikarma tat ||</p> 
