                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">atha dhautī |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">mṛdulaṃ dhavalaṃ śuddhaṃ caturaṅgulavistṛtam |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">tithihastamitāyāmaṃ dhautīvastrasya lakṣaṇam ||</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">toyasiktaṃ grased vastraṃ ghrāṇābhyāṃ vāyum utsṛjan |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">śanaiḥ sanais tu sakalaṃ punaḥ pratyāharec chanaiḥ |</p>
