            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               dhautikarmaṇaḥ phalam āha kāsaśvāseti. kāsaś ca śvāsaś ca plīhaś ca kuṣṭhaṃ ca. samāhāradvandvaḥ
               kāsādayo rogaviśeṣāḥ viṃśatiḥ viṃśatisaṅkhyākāḥ kapharogāś ca dhautikarmaṇaḥ prabhāveṇa
               gacchanty
               eva na saṃśayaḥ niścitam etad ity arthaḥ.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               dhautikarmaṇaḥ phalam āha kāsaśvāseti. kāsaś ca śvāsaś ca plīhaś ca kuṣṭhaṃ ca. samāhāradvandvaḥ
               kāsādayo rogaviśeṣāḥ viṃśatiḥ viṃśatisaṅkhyākāḥ kapharogāś ca dhautikarmaṇaḥ prabhāveṇa
               gacchanty
               eva na saṃśayaḥ niścitam etad ity arthaḥ.
               </div>
