                  </div>
               ity amaraḥ. savyaṃ cāpasavyaṃ ca savyāpasavye dakṣiṇavāmabhāgau tayoḥ
               savyāpasavyataḥ. saptamyarthe tasiḥ. bhrāmayed bhramantaṃ prerayet. siddhair eṣā nauliḥ
               pracakṣyate kathyate.
