      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_037" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.37</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>षट्कर्मभिर्गत</mark><mark>स्थौल्य</mark>कफ<mark>मेदो</mark><mark>मलादिकः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> प्राणायामं ततः कुर्याद् अनायासेन <mark>सिध्यति</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>ṣaṭkarmabhir gata</mark><mark>sthaulya</mark>kapha<mark>medo</mark><mark>malādikaḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> prāṇāyāmaṃ tataḥ kuryād anāyāsena <mark>sidhyati</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> The person whose excess weight, phlegm, fat, impurities and the like have been removed
               by the six techniques should then perform breath-control. It succeeds without effort.
