   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_048" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.48</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>तत्र</mark> <mark>सूर्यभेदनम्</mark>  । 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>आसने सुखदे योगी</mark> <mark>बद्ध्वा</mark> <mark>वज्रासनं</mark> <mark>ततः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> दक्ष<mark>नाड्या</mark> समाकृष्य <mark>बहिःस्थं</mark> पवनं शनैः ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>tatra</mark> <mark>sūryabhedanam</mark> / 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>āsane sukhade yogī</mark> <mark>baddhvā</mark> <mark>vajrāsanaṃ</mark> <mark>tataḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> dakṣa<mark>nāḍyā</mark> samākṛṣya <mark>bahiḥsthaṃ</mark> pavanaṃ śanaiḥ //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Now, piercing the sun---The yogi should sit in <i>vajrāsana</i> on a comfortable mat, slowly draw in external air through the right nostril, [...]
               </div>
