            <details class="testimonia-d">
               <summary>Testimonia</summary>
               <div class="testimonia"> <i>Yogalakṣaṇāvalī</i> f.~32r (attrib. to the <i>Haṭhapradīpikā</i>) 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">ā nakhāgrālakāgrāntaṃ kumbhayitvā yathāsukham |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">savyanāḍyā tato mandaṃ recayet pavanaṃ sudhīḥ ||</p> 
                     </div>
                  <i>Yogacintāmaṇi</i> f.~101v (attr.~to the <i>Yogabīja</i>) 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">ā keśāgraṃ nakhāgraṃ ca śirodhāvadhi kumbhakam |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">tataḥ śanaiḥ savyanāḍyā recayet pavanaṃ sudhīḥ ||</p> 
                     </div>
                  <i>Yuktabhavadeva</i> 7.99 (attr.~to the <i>Haṭhapradīpikā</i>) 
                  <div class="lg">
                     <p class="versinnote">ā keśād ā nakhāgrāc ca nirodhāvadhi kumbhayet |</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">tataḥ śanaiḥ savyanāḍyā recayet pavanaṃ sudhīḥ ||</p> 
                     </div>
                  </div>
            </details>
