               vivardhanaṃ
               viśeṣeṇa vardhanaṃ dīpanam ity arthaḥ.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               pūrvavad iti. prāṇaṃ pūrvavat pūrveṇa sūryabhedanena tulyaṃ pūrvavat. ākeśād ānakhāgrāc
               ca
               nirodhāvadhi kumbhayed ityuktarītyā kumbhayed rodhayet. tataḥ kumbhakānantaram iḍayā
               vāmanāḍyā
               recayet tyajet.  prāṇaṃ pūrvavat pūrveṇa sūryabhedanena tulyaṃ pūrvavat. ākeśād ānakhāgrāc
               ca
               nirodhāvadhi kumbhayed ityuktarītyā kumbhayed rodhayet. tataḥ kumbhakānantaram iḍayā
               vāmanāḍyā
               recayet tyajet.
               ujjāyiguṇān āha sārdhaślokena śleṣmadoṣaharam iti. kaṇṭhe kaṇṭhapradeśe śleṣmaṇo doṣāḥ
