         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_055" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.55</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> योगिनी<mark>चक्रसामान्यः</mark> सृष्टिसंहारकारकः ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> न क्षुधा न तृषा निद्रा <mark>नैवालस्यं</mark> <mark>प्रजायते</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> yoginī<mark>cakrasāmānyaḥ</mark> sṛṣṭisaṃhārakārakaḥ /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> na kṣudhā na tṛṣā nidrā <mark>naivālasyaṃ</mark> <mark>prajāyate</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> He joins the circle of yoginis and brings about creation and destruction. Neither
               hunger nor thirst [nor] sleep nor indolence arise [for him]. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
