      <details class="jyotsna-d">
         <summary>Jyotsna Commentary
            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               yoginīnāṃ cakraṃ yoginīcakraṃ yoginīsamūhaḥ. tasya samṃmānyaḥ saṃsevyaḥ. sṛṣṭiḥ prapañcotpattiḥ
               saṃhāras tallayaḥ tayoḥ kārakaḥ kartā. kṣudhā bhoktum icchā na. tṛṣā jalapānecchā
               na. nidrā
               suṣuptir na. ālasyaṃ kāyacittagauravāt pravṛttyabhāvaḥ. kāyagauravaṃ kaphādinā cittagauravaṃ
               tamoguṇena. naiva prajāyate naiva prādurbhavati. evam abhyāsayogeneti prajāyata iti
               ca prativākyaṃ
               sambadhyate.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               yoginīnāṃ cakraṃ yoginīcakraṃ yoginīsamūhaḥ. tasya samṃmānyaḥ saṃsevyaḥ. sṛṣṭiḥ prapañcotpattiḥ
               saṃhāras tallayaḥ tayoḥ kārakaḥ kartā. kṣudhā bhoktum icchā na. tṛṣā jalapānecchā
               na. nidrā
               suṣuptir na. ālasyaṃ kāyacittagauravāt pravṛttyabhāvaḥ. kāyagauravaṃ kaphādinā cittagauravaṃ
               tamoguṇena. naiva prajāyate naiva prādurbhavati. evam abhyāsayogeneti prajāyata iti
               ca prativākyaṃ
               sambadhyate.
