      <details class="jyotsna-d">
         <summary>Jyotsna Commentary
            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               bhaved iti. dehasya śarīrasya sattvaṃ balaṃ ca bhavet. anenoktena vidhinābhyāsavidhinā
               yogīndro
               yoginām indra iva yogīndro bhūmimaṇḍale sarvair upadravair varjitaḥ sarvopadravavarjito
               bhavet
               satyam. sarvaṃ vākyaṃ sāvadhāraṇam iti nyāyāt. yad uktaṃ phalaṃ tat satyam evety arthaḥ.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               bhaved iti. dehasya śarīrasya sattvaṃ balaṃ ca bhavet. anenoktena vidhinābhyāsavidhinā
               yogīndro
               yoginām indra iva yogīndro bhūmimaṇḍale sarvair upadravair varjitaḥ sarvopadravavarjito
               bhavet
               satyam. sarvaṃ vākyaṃ sāvadhāraṇam iti nyāyāt. yad uktaṃ phalaṃ tat satyam evety arthaḥ.
               </div>
