   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_058" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.58</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>अथ</mark> <mark>शीतली</mark> । 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>जिह्वया</mark> वायु<mark>माकृष्य</mark> <mark>पूर्वव</mark><mark>त्कुम्भकादनु</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>शनैस्तु</mark> <mark>घ्राण</mark>रन्ध्राभ्यां रेचये<mark>दनिलं</mark> <mark>सुधीः</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>atha</mark> <mark>śītalī</mark> / 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>jihvayā</mark> vāyu<mark>m ākṛṣya</mark> <mark>pūrvava</mark><mark>t kumbhakād anu</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>śanais tu</mark> <mark>ghrāṇa</mark>randhrābhyāṃ recaye<mark>d anilaṃ</mark> <mark>sudhīḥ</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Now śītalī:The wise man should draw in air through the tongue and after retaining
               the breath as before gradually exhale through the nostrils . </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
