      <details class="jyotsna-d">
         <summary>Jyotsna Commentary
            	  </summary>
         <div class="jyotsna">
            <div class="versdev">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               śītalīkumbhakam āha jihvayeti. jihvayā oṣṭhayor bahir nirgatayā vihaṅgamādharacañcusadṛśayā
               vāyum
               ākṛṣya śanaiḥ pūrakaṃ kṛtvety arthaḥ. pūrvavat sūryabhedanavat kumbhasya kumbhakasya
               sādhanaṃm
               vidhānaṃ kṛtvety adhyāhāraḥ. sudhīḥ śobhanā dhīr yasya saḥ. ghrāṇasya randhre ghrāṇarandhre
               tābhyāṃ
               nāsāpuṭavivarābhyāṃ śanakaiḥ śanair eva. avyayasarvanāmnām ity
               akac. pavanaṃ vāyum recayet.
               </div>
            <div class="versltn">
               <div class="lg">
                  </div>
               śītalīkumbhakam āha jihvayeti. jihvayā oṣṭhayor bahir nirgatayā vihaṅgamādharacañcusadṛśayā
               vāyum
               ākṛṣya śanaiḥ pūrakaṃ kṛtvety arthaḥ. pūrvavat sūryabhedanavat kumbhasya kumbhakasya
               sādhanaṃm
               vidhānaṃ kṛtvety adhyāhāraḥ. sudhīḥ śobhanā dhīr yasya saḥ. ghrāṇasya randhre ghrāṇarandhre
               tābhyāṃ
               nāsāpuṭavivarābhyāṃ śanakaiḥ śanair eva. avyayasarvanāmnām ity
               akac. pavanaṃ vāyum recayet.
               </div>
