   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp02_060" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 2.60</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>अथ</mark> <mark>भस्त्रिका</mark> । 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> ऊर्वोरुपरि <mark>चेद्धत्ते</mark> <mark>उभे</mark> पादतले <mark>तथा</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> पद्मासनं भवे<mark>त्सम्य</mark>क् सर्वपापप्रणाशनम् ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>atha</mark> <mark>bhastrikā</mark> / 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> ūrvor upari <mark>ced dhatte</mark> <mark>ubhe</mark> pādatale <mark>tathā</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> padmāsanaṃ bhave<mark>t samya</mark>k sarvapāpapraṇāśanam //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Now bhastrikā: If [the yogi] places the soles of both feet on the thighs, the lotus
               pose, which destroys all bad deeds, duly arises. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
