               <div class="app"><span class="lem">yoga</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] haṭha (<span class="siglum" title="β1 β2 βω C6,P11,V3">β<sub>1</sub> β<sub>2</sub> β<sub>ω</sub></span>), <i>om.</i> (<span class="siglum" title="δ2 Privat collection">δ<sub>2</sub></span>)</div>
