            <div id="hp03_003" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.3</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>प्राणस्य</mark> शून्य<mark>पदवी</mark><span class="fn" title="ε1, ε2 and ε3 jump to śūnyapadavī in the next verse."><b>*</b></span>
