      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_004" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.4</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>शून्यपदवीति किम्</mark> । 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> सुषुम्णा शून्यपदवी ब्रह्म<mark>रन्ध्र</mark>महा<mark>पथः</mark> । 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>श्मशानं</mark> शाम्भवी <mark>मध्य</mark><mark>मार्गश्चेत्येक</mark><mark>वाचकाः</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>śūnyapadavīti kim</mark> / 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> suṣumṇā śūnyapadavī brahma<mark>randhra</mark>mahā<mark>pathaḥ</mark> / 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>śmaśānaṃ</mark> śāmbhavī <mark>madhya</mark><mark>mārgaś cety eka</mark><mark>vācakāḥ</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> <i>Suṣumṇā</i>, the empty pathway, the great path to the aperture of Brahmā, the cremation ground,
               Śāmbhavī, and the middle path are synonyms. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="metre">
               	      Metre:  Anuṣṭubh (a: na-vipulā) </div>
            <div class="apparatus">
