      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_005" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.5</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> तस्मात्सर्वप्रयत्नेन <mark>प्रबोधयितु</mark><mark>मीश्वरीम्</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> ब्रह्म<mark>द्वार</mark><mark>मुखे</mark> <mark>सुप्तां</mark> मुद्रा<mark>भ्यासं समाचरेत्</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> tasmāt sarvaprayatnena <mark>prabodhayitu</mark><mark>m īśvarīm</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> brahma<mark>dvāra</mark><mark>mukhe</mark> <mark>suptāṃ</mark> mudrā<mark>bhyāsaṃ samācaret</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Therefore, in order to do his utmost to awaken the goddess sleeping in front of the
               doorway of Brahman, [the yogi] should carry out the practice of <i>mudrā</i>. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
