         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_006" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.6</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> महामुद्रा महाबन्धो महावेधश्च खेचरी ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>उड्डियानं</mark> मूल<mark>बन्धो</mark> <mark>बन्धो</mark> <mark>जालन्धरा</mark>भिधः ॥ 
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> mahāmudrā mahābandho mahāvedhaś ca khecarī /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>uḍḍiyānaṃ</mark> mūla<mark>bandho</mark> <mark>bandho</mark> <mark>jālandharā</mark>bhidhaḥ // 
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> The great seal, the great lock, the great piercing, the sky-roving [seal], the <i>uḍḍiyāna</i> [lock], the root lock and the lock called <i>jālandhara</i>, [dots ] </div>
         </div>
