            <div id="hp03_007" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.7</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>करणी</mark> <mark>विपरीताख्या</mark> <mark>वज्रोली</mark> शक्तिचालनम् । </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>इदं मुद्रादि</mark>दशकं जरा<mark>मरण</mark><mark>नाशनम्</mark> ॥ 
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>karaṇī</mark> <mark>viparītākhyā</mark> <mark>vajrolī</mark> śakticālanam / </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>idaṃ mudrādi</mark>daśakaṃ jarā<mark>maraṇa</mark><mark>nāśanam</mark> // 
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> [ldots ] the bodily position called inverted, <i>vajrolī</i> [and] the stimulation of the goddess: this group of ten <i>mudrā</i>s and other [practices] destroys old age and death. </div>
         </div>
