                     <p class="hpvers"> वज्रोली <mark>त्वमरोली</mark> च <mark>सहजोली</mark> त्रिधा <mark>मताः</mark> । </p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> <mark>एतेषां</mark> लक्षणं <mark>वक्ष्ये</mark> कर्तव्यं च विशेषतः ॥ <span class="inlineref">(<span class="siglum" title="β2 Lalchand M-2089">β<sub>2</sub></span>, <span class="siglum" title="βω Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 29899">β<sub>ω</sub></span> and <span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span>)</span>
                        </p> 
