   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_010" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.10</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>तत्र महामुद्रा</mark> । </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> पादमूलेन वामेन <mark>योनिं</mark> <mark>संपीड्य</mark> दक्षिणम् ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>पादं</mark> <mark>प्रसारितं</mark> <mark>धृत्वा</mark> कराभ्यां <mark>पूरये</mark><mark>न्मुखे</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>tatra mahāmudrā</mark> / </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> pādamūlena vāmena <mark>yoniṃ</mark> <mark>saṃpīḍya</mark> dakṣiṇam /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>pādaṃ</mark> <mark>prasāritaṃ</mark> <mark>dhṛtvā</mark> karābhyāṃ <mark>pūraye</mark><mark>n mukhe</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Now the great seal (<i>mahāmudrā</i>):{}[The yogi] should press the perineum with the heel of the left foot, hold [the
               foot of] the extended leg with the hands and breathe in through the mouth. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
