      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_016" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.16</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>न हि पथ्यमपथ्यं वा</mark> रसाः सर्वेऽपि नीरसाः ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>अपि भुक्तं</mark> <mark>विषं घोरं</mark> <mark>पीयूष</mark><mark>मिव</mark> <mark>जीर्यते</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>na hi pathyam apathyaṃ vā</mark> rasāḥ sarve’pi nīrasāḥ /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>api bhuktaṃ</mark> <mark>viṣaṃ ghoraṃ</mark> <mark>pīyūṣa</mark><mark>m iva</mark> <mark>jīryate</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> {}[For the yogi who practises thus] there is no wholesome or unwholesome [food],
               and all flavours without exception become flavourless. Even terrible poison, when
               consumed, is digested like nectar. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
