            <div id="hp03_017" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.17</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> क्षय<mark>कुष्ठ</mark><mark>गुदा</mark>वर्त<mark>गुल्माजीर्ण</mark><mark>पुरोगमाः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>तस्य दोषाः</mark> क्षयं यान्ति महामुद्रां <mark>तु योऽभ्यसेत्</mark> ॥ 
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> kṣaya<mark>kuṣṭha</mark><mark>gudā</mark>varta<mark>gulmājīrṇa</mark><mark>purogamāḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>tasya doṣāḥ</mark> kṣayaṃ yānti mahāmudrāṃ <mark>tu yo’bhyaset</mark> // 
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Diseases such as consumption, skin afflictions, constipation, swelling and indigestion
               disappear for [the yogi] who practises the great seal. </div>
