      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_023" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.23</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>अयं</mark> <mark>खलु</mark> महा<mark>बन्धो</mark> <mark>महा</mark>सिद्धि<mark>प्रदायकः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> काल<mark>पाश</mark>महा<mark>बन्ध</mark><mark>विमोचन</mark><mark>विचक्षणः</mark> ॥<span class="fn" title="χ has a different verse order: ab rightarrow  abcd rightarrow  cd."><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>ayaṃ</mark> <mark>khalu</mark> mahā<mark>bandho</mark> <mark>mahā</mark>siddhi<mark>pradāyakaḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> kāla<mark>pāśa</mark>mahā<mark>bandha</mark><mark>vimocana</mark><mark>vicakṣaṇaḥ</mark> //<span class="fn" title="χ has a different verse order: ab rightarrow  abcd rightarrow  cd."><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> This is truly the great lock: it bestows the great <i>siddhi</i> [and] is adept at loosening the great bond (<i>°mahābandha°</i>) that is the noose of time. </div>
         </div>
