               <div class="app"><span class="lem">pradāyakaḥ</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] pradāyakaṃ (<span class="siglum" title="α1 NGMPP B 62-20 α1ac α1pc">α<sub>1</sub></span>)</div>
