   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_026" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.26</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>अथ महावेधः</mark> । 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>महाबन्ध</mark><mark>स्थितो</mark> योगी कृत्वा पूरक<mark>मेकधीः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>वायूनां</mark> <mark>गतिमावृत्य</mark> निभृतं कण्ठ<mark>मुद्रया</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="avataranika"> <mark>atha mahāvedhaḥ</mark> / 
                     </p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>mahābandha</mark><mark>sthito</mark> yogī kṛtvā pūraka<mark>m ekadhīḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>vāyūnāṃ</mark> <mark>gatim āvṛtya</mark> nibhṛtaṃ kaṇṭha<mark>mudrayā</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> While in the great lock, the yogi should inhale, focus his mind and firmly block
               the flow of the bodily winds by means of the throat seal. </div>
            <details class="philcomm-d">
               <summary>Philological Commentary</summary>
               <div class="philcomm"> We are not certain of the meaning of <i>nibhṛtam</i>, which is found in all of the collated witnesses and important testimonia. We have
                  understood it as an adverb meaning `firmly.’ </div>
            </details>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">atha mahāvedhaḥ</span> (<span class="siglum" title="βω Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 29899">β<sub>ω</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε3 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30051 ε3ac ε3pc">ε<sub>3</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="χ Brahmānanda’s version">χ</span>) ] found before  (<span class="siglum" title="β2 Lalchand M-2089">β<sub>2</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="δ3 Lalchand M-6494">δ<sub>3</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε2 NGMPP E-1528-1 / E-1527-7(4)">ε<sub>2</sub></span>), mahāvedhaḥ (found before ) (<span class="siglum" title="Γ N23,J7">Γ</span> <span class="siglum" title="δ2 Privat collection">δ<sub>2</sub></span>), iti mahābandhaḥ (<span class="siglum" title="η1 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30109 η1ac η1pc">η<sub>1</sub></span>), atha mahābaṃdhaḥ (found after ab) (<span class="siglum" title="α2 Jodhpur 02235">α<sub>2</sub></span>), <i>om.</i> (<span class="siglum" title="α1 NGMPP B 62-20 α1ac α1pc">α<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="β1">β<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="δ1 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30069">δ<sub>1</sub></span>)</div>
