            <div id="hp03_030" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.30</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>एतत्त्रयं महा</mark><mark>गुह्यं</mark> जरामृत्यु<mark>विनाशनम्</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> वह्निवृद्धिकरं <mark>चैव</mark> अणिमादि<mark>गुण</mark><mark>प्रदम्</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>etat trayaṃ mahā</mark><mark>guhyaṃ</mark> jarāmṛtyu<mark>vināśanam</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> vahnivṛddhikaraṃ <mark>caiva</mark> aṇimādi<mark>guṇa</mark><mark>pradam</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> This triad is a great secret that destroys old and death, increases [the body’s]
               fire and bestows the powers beginning with minimisation. </div>
