   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_031" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.31</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> अष्टधा क्रियते <mark>चैत</mark><mark>द्यामे यामे</mark> दिने दिने ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>पुण्य</mark><mark>संभार</mark><mark>सम्भावि</mark> <mark>पापौघ</mark><mark>भिदुरं सदा</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> aṣṭadhā kriyate <mark>caita</mark><mark>d yāme yāme</mark> dine dine /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>puṇya</mark><mark>saṃbhāra</mark><mark>sambhāvi</mark> <mark>pāpaugha</mark><mark>bhiduraṃ sadā</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> It is practised eight times a day, every three hours. It always produces a wealth
               of merit and destroys an ocean of demerit. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
