            <div id="hp03_032" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.32</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> सम्यक्<mark>शिक्षावता</mark><mark>मेव</mark> स्वल्पं प्रथम<mark>साधने</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> वह्निस्त्रीपथ<mark>सेवाना</mark>मादौ वर्जन<mark>मादिशेत्</mark> ॥<span class="fn" title="Γ adds here: mahāmudrā mahābandho mahāvedhaś ca nityaśaḥ / etat trayaṃ prayatnena caturvāraṃ karoti yaḥ / ṣaṇmāsābhyantare mṛtyuṃ jayaty eva na saṃśayaḥ // (= Śivasaṃhitā xx)"><b>*</b></span>
                     <span class="fn" title="χ has this line just after ."><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> samyak<mark>śikṣāvatā</mark><mark>m eva</mark> svalpaṃ prathama<mark>sādhane</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> vahnistrīpatha<mark>sevānā</mark>m ādau varjana<mark>m ādiśet</mark> //<span class="fn" title="Γ adds here: mahāmudrā mahābandho mahāvedhaś ca nityaśaḥ / etat trayaṃ prayatnena caturvāraṃ karoti yaḥ / ṣaṇmāsābhyantare mṛtyuṃ jayaty eva na saṃśayaḥ // (= Śivasaṃhitā xx)"><b>*</b></span>
                     <span class="fn" title="χ has this line just after ."><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> It is only for those who have received proper instruction. It is taught that they
               should [do it] a little in the first stage of the practice [and] that at the beginning
               [the yogi] should avoid frequenting fire, women and roads. </div>
         </div>
