                     <p class="hpvers"> नासनं सिद्धसदृशं न <mark>कुम्भं</mark> <mark>केवलोपमम्</mark> ।</p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> न खेचरीसमा मुद्रा न नादसदृशो लयः ॥ <span class="inlineref">(<span class="siglum" title="Ω V3,J6,N9,N26">Ω</span>)</span>
                        </p> 
                     </div>
                  <div class="versltn">
                     <p class="hpvers"> nāsanaṃ siddhasadṛśaṃ na <mark>kumbhaṃ</mark> <mark>kevalopamam</mark> /</p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> na khecarīsamā mudrā na nādasadṛśo layaḥ // <span class="inlineref">(<span class="siglum" title="Ω V3,J6,N9,N26">Ω</span>)</span>
                        </p> 
