      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_034" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.34</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> कपाल<mark>कुहरे</mark> जिह्वा <mark>प्रविष्टा विपरीतगा</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> भ्रुवो<mark>रन्तर्गता</mark> <mark>दृष्टि</mark>र् मुद्रा भवति <mark>खेचरी</mark> ॥<span class="fn" title="χ has this verse at the very beginning of the Khecarī-section."><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> kapāla<mark>kuhare</mark> jihvā <mark>praviṣṭā viparītagā</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> bhruvo<mark>r antargatā</mark> <mark>dṛṣṭi</mark>r mudrā bhavati <mark>khecarī</mark> //<span class="fn" title="χ has this verse at the very beginning of the Khecarī-section."><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> When the tongue is turned back and inserted into the cavity of the skull and the
               gaze is between the brows, <i>khecarīmudrā</i> arises. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">kuhare</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] vivare (<span class="siglum" title="β1">β<sub>1</sub></span>)</div>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">praviṣṭā viparītagā</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] pra + + + + + + (<span class="siglum" title="α1 NGMPP B 62-20 α1ac α1pc">α<sub>1</sub></span>)</div>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">antargatā</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] aṃtagatā (<span class="siglum" title="α1 NGMPP B 62-20 α1ac α1pc">α<sub>1</sub></span>), madhagatā (<span class="siglum" title="β1">β<sub>1</sub></span>), madhye gatā (<span class="siglum" title="β2 Lalchand M-2089">β<sub>2</sub></span>)</div>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">dṛṣṭir</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] dṛṣṭi (<span class="siglum" title="α1 NGMPP B 62-20 α1ac α1pc">α<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="β1">β<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="γ1 NGMPP G 25-2 γ1ac γ1pc">γ<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε3 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30051 ε3ac ε3pc">ε<sub>3</sub></span>)</div>
