         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_036" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.36</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> न <mark>रोगो</mark> मरणं <mark>तस्य</mark> न निद्रा न <mark>क्षुधा तृषा</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> न <mark>च</mark> मूर्छा <mark>भवे</mark><mark>त्तस्य</mark> <mark>यो मुद्रां वेत्ति</mark> <mark>खेचरीम्</mark> ॥<span class="fn" title="In γ2 this verse is found after ."><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> na <mark>rogo</mark> maraṇaṃ <mark>tasya</mark> na nidrā na <mark>kṣudhā tṛṣā</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> na <mark>ca</mark> mūrchā <mark>bhave</mark><mark>t tasya</mark> <mark>yo mudrāṃ vetti</mark> <mark>khecarīm</mark> //<span class="fn" title="In γ2 this verse is found after ."><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> For the yogi who knows <i>khecarīmudrā</i> there is no disease, death, sleep, hunger, thirst or fainting. </div>
         </div>
