   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_039" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.39</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>खेचर्या</mark> <mark>मुद्रितं</mark> येन <mark>विवरं</mark> <mark>लम्बिकोर्ध्वतः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>तस्य न</mark> क्षरते बिन्दुः कामिन्या<mark>श्लेषितस्य</mark> च ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>khecaryā</mark> <mark>mudritaṃ</mark> yena <mark>vivaraṃ</mark> <mark>lambikordhvataḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>tasya na</mark> kṣarate binduḥ kāminyā<mark>śleṣitasya</mark> ca //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> The yogi who has sealed the cavity above the uvula with <i>khecarī</i> does not lose his semen [even if] embraced by an amorous woman. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
