                     <p class="versinnote">gacchaty ūrdhvaṃ hataḥ śaktyā nibaddho yonimudrayā ||</p>
                     <p class="versinnote">53c <span class="appinnote">gacchaty ] vrajaty <i>v.l.</i>53d hataḥ ] tanaṃ, hṛtas, kṛte, kṛtaḥ, tadā, gatā <i>v.l.</i>• nibaddho ] niruddho <i>v.l.</i></span>
                        </p> 
                     </div>
