   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_041" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.41</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>ऊर्ध्व</mark><mark>जिह्वः</mark> <mark>स्थितो</mark> भूत्वा सोमपानं <mark>करोति यः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>मासार्धेन न</mark> संदेहो मृत्युं जयति योगवित् ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>ūrdhva</mark><mark>jihvaḥ</mark> <mark>sthito</mark> bhūtvā somapānaṃ <mark>karoti yaḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>māsārdhena na</mark> saṃdeho mṛtyuṃ jayati yogavit //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> The knower of yoga who remains with the tongue upwards and drinks nectar certainly
               conquers death in half a month. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">ūrdhva</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] ūrdhvaṃ (<span class="siglum" title="α3 GOML 18885">α<sub>3</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε2 NGMPP E-1528-1 / E-1527-7(4)">ε<sub>2</sub></span>)</div>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">jihvaḥ</span> (<span class="siglum" title="γ2 Jodhpur 02241">γ<sub>2</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="δ1 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30069">δ<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="δ3 Lalchand M-6494">δ<sub>3</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="χ Brahmānanda’s version">χ</span>) ] jihva (<span class="siglum" title="γ1 NGMPP G 25-2 γ1ac γ1pc">γ<sub>1</sub></span>), jihvā (<span class="siglum" title="α1 NGMPP B 62-20 α1ac α1pc">α<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="β1 β2 βω C6,P11,V3">β<sub>1</sub> β<sub>2</sub> β<sub>ω</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="δ2 Privat collection">δ<sub>2</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε2 NGMPP E-1528-1 / E-1527-7(4)">ε<sub>2</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε3 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30051 ε3ac ε3pc">ε<sub>3</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="η1 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30109 η1ac η1pc">η<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span>)</div>
