               <div class="app"><span class="lem">pūrṇaṃ</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] pūrṇa (<span class="siglum" title="β1">β<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="γ1 NGMPP G 25-2 γ1ac γ1pc">γ<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="ε2 NGMPP E-1528-1 / E-1527-7(4)">ε<sub>2</sub></span>), pūrṇe (<span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span>)</div>
