               <div class="app"><span class="lem">viṣaṃ tasya na</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] viṣeṇa na hi (<span class="siglum" title="α3 GOML 18885">α<sub>3</sub></span>)</div>
