      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_043" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.43</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>इन्धनानि</mark> <mark>यथा</mark> वह्नि<mark>स्तैलवर्तिं</mark> <mark>च</mark> <mark>दीपकः</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> तथा <mark>सोम</mark>कला<mark>पूर्णं</mark> <mark>देही देहं</mark> <mark>न मुञ्चति</mark> ॥<span class="fn" title="Γ and Δ add here: rasanāṃ veśayed ūrdhvaṃ pibet tat srāvitaṃ jalam"><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>indhanāni</mark> <mark>yathā</mark> vahni<mark>s tailavartiṃ</mark> <mark>ca</mark> <mark>dīpakaḥ</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> tathā <mark>soma</mark>kalā<mark>pūrṇaṃ</mark> <mark>dehī dehaṃ</mark> <mark>na muñcati</mark> //<span class="fn" title="Γ and Δ add here: rasanāṃ veśayed ūrdhvaṃ pibet tat srāvitaṃ jalam"><b>*</b></span>
                     </p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> Just as fire does not leave its fuel nor light a wick in oil, so the embodied person
               does not leave a body filled by the digits of the moon. </div>
         </div>
