   <div class="main">
      <div class="hpmeta">
         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_044" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.44</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>गोमांसं</mark> भक्षयेन्नित्यं पिबे<mark>दमर</mark><mark>वारुणीम्</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> कुलीनं <mark>त</mark>महं <mark>मन्ये</mark> <mark>इतरे</mark> <mark>कुलघातकाः</mark> ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>gomāṃsaṃ</mark> bhakṣayen nityaṃ pibe<mark>d amara</mark><mark>vāruṇīm</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> kulīnaṃ <mark>ta</mark>m ahaṃ <mark>manye</mark> <mark>itare</mark> <mark>kulaghātakāḥ</mark> //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> I consider he who regularly eats cow flesh and drinks God’s liquor to be of good
               family. Others are destroyers of the family. </div>
         </div>
         <div class="crit">
            <div class="apparatus">
               <h3>Readings</h3>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">gomāṃsaṃ</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] gomāṃsa (<span class="siglum" title="γ2 Jodhpur 02241">γ<sub>2</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="δ1 Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 30069">δ<sub>1</sub></span> <span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span>)</div>
               <div class="app"><span class="lem">amara</span> (<span class="siglum" title="cett. ceteri">cett.</span>) ] amṛta (<span class="siglum" title="δ3 Lalchand M-6494">δ<sub>3</sub></span>)</div>
