               <div id="hp03_049_1" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.49*1</span><div class="versdev">
                     <p class="hpvers"> <mark>सुषिरं</mark> ज्ञानजनकं पञ्च<mark>स्रोतः</mark>समन्वितम् ।</p>
                     <p class="hpvers"> <mark>तिष्ठते</mark> खेचरी मुद्रा तस्मिन्शून्ये निरञ्जने ॥ <span class="inlineref">(<span class="siglum" title="βω Sampurnananda Library Sarasvati Bhavan 29899">β<sub>ω</sub></span>, <span class="siglum" title="η2 MSPP Jodhpur 2230 η2ac η2pc">η<sub>2</sub></span> and <span class="siglum" title="χ Brahmānanda’s version">χ</span>)</span>
                        </p> 
                     </div>
                  <div class="versltn">
                     <p class="hpvers"> <mark>suṣiraṃ</mark> jñānajanakaṃ pañca<mark>srotaḥ</mark>samanvitam /</p>
