         <div class="text">
            <div id="hp03_051" class="hp"><span class="number">HP 3.51</span><div class="versdev">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>अधोगति</mark><mark>मपानं वै</mark> <mark>ऊर्ध्वगं</mark> कुरुते <mark>बलात्</mark> ।</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>आकुञ्चनेन</mark> <mark>तं</mark> <mark>प्राहु</mark><mark>र्मूलबन्धं</mark> <mark>तु</mark> योगिनः ॥</p> 
                  </div>
               <div class="versltn">
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>adhogati</mark><mark>m apānaṃ vai</mark> <mark>ūrdhvagaṃ</mark> kurute <mark>balāt</mark> /</p>
                  <p class="hpvers"> <mark>ākuñcanena</mark> <mark>taṃ</mark> <mark>prāhu</mark><mark>r mūlabandhaṃ</mark> <mark>tu</mark> yoginaḥ //</p> 
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="translation"> [The yogi] forces the downward-moving <i>apāna</i> breath to move upwards by contracting [the anus]. Yogis call that <i>mūlabandha</i>. </div>
